The paper discusses deep generative modeling using flows, which is a topic that falls under the machine learning and computer vision domains. The paper proposes a novel multi-scale architecture for generative flows, which is likely to be of interest to researchers working in the areas of deep learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and statistical learning (cs.SD).
